data.title: The Brooklyn Paper. Media Archives
data.meta_description: Interviews, reviews and articles from Stephen Wiltshire's media archive from The Brooklyn Paper to Yedioth Ahronoth IV.
data.text:
Shopping

Pay with your credit or debit card, PayPal, Bank Transfer, Apple Pay or Google Pay. We ship worldwide on a daily basis and you can also buy original drawings for collection at our Private London Gallery. Payment Methods

Delivery

We deliver worldwide on a daily basis while your parcel is fully covered by our Lloyds policy throughout its journey. Shipping costs start from £7.99 within UK and £15.99 to anywhere in the world depending dimensions and weight. All parcels are packaged professionally. More on Shipping

Commission the Artist

Stephen continues to take on art commissions for his clientele. Call, message or email us if you have a particular view or city in mind. There may be a waiting list. Commissions

Press office

Information for journalists and publishers about Stephen Wiltshire, including press releases, key dates, biography, his rider, Q&A and publishing rights. Our Archive and Image Library are also available to you. Brief us about the context and direction of your publication or Message Us to schedule an interview. Press Office

Returns

If for any reason you are unhappy with your purchase, let us know within 21 days, and we will offer you a full refund, no questions asked. We replace your items in case your parcel is damaged or lost in transit. Shop with Confidence
